{"tid":100125,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"PC 打機更流暢！Microsoft 將推出 Windows 10 專用的「遊戲模式」","createTime":"2017-01-29T17:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T17:37:57.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5ec5fb9a353efe39a74ab8476ed5fc4b5df530","tid":100125,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:29:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/01/26/windows-10-game-mode/software/win10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2Fwindows-10-game-mode%2Fsoftware%2Fwin10%2F&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=aa129f49\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/01/26/windows-10-game-mode/software/win10/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/001-150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F001-150.jpg&h=26820d3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年底有網民發現 Windows 10 將會加入「遊戲模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」（Game Mode），由於系統會優先將資源分配到遊戲中，因此將可以令打機變得更流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。雖然除此之外就沒有太多情報，不過今日 Microsoft 公開了一段最新影片，並講解遊戲模式到底如何運作，而 Windows 10 Builds 將可以在明日開始用到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/002-108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F002-108.jpg&h=c86e8135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據 Microsoft 表示當系統進入遊戲模式後，CPU 及 GPU 資源將會優先分配到遊戲內，無需擔心會被其他執行中的工作拖累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，相信其最終目的應該是希望改善每一款遊戲的畫面更新率，從而令遊戲運行得更流暢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。此外，影片中同時亦顯示除遊戲模式外，Windows 10 亦將會加入多項與遊戲相關的新功能，比如按下「Windows + G」會開啟 Game Bar，提供快捷鍵讓玩家截圖及錄影等，另外亦內置 Beam 串流直播，分享打機內容變得方便得多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/003-71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F003-71.jpg&h=8c4ba4be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留意遊戲模式主要根據逐款遊戲來啟用，若然玩家想開啟此模式，首先需要在遊戲中開啟 Game Bar，然後再在選單中選擇 Game Mode 並將之開啟，接著再返回遊戲便可以提高效能。此外，Microsoft 表示將來部份遊戲將可支援自動執行遊戲模式，但現階段並非太多遊戲可以做到，而上述功能將會在稍後時間的 Windows 10 Creators 更新中推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/004-51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F004-51.jpg&h=8b8699bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zc-ka42BMls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZc-ka42BMls&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=3d5fd931\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zc-ka42BMls</a>"},{"pid":"61e1d43559f3ff9adf5e7aab5715bf290fce40db","tid":100125,"uid":159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:35:47.000Z","msg":"會有幾大分別呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPC打到機既硬件本身都唔會差得去邊"},{"pid":"e5c77a1bb62d6a1cbd5aa4e986969f8788837203","tid":100125,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:37:12.000Z","msg":"樓主24小時上連登。。。"},{"pid":"c73b375eb5274f42fb7349f57f5380078b9165e9","tid":100125,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主24小時上連登。。。</blockquote><br />\n邊有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}